<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA21">
<l>ceṉṟaṅku vennarakil cērāmaṟ kāppataṟ</l>
<l>kiṉṟiṅkeṉ ṉeñcā liṭukkuṇṭa vaṉṟaṅkup</l>
<l>pāruruvum pārvaḷaitta nīruruvuṅ kaṇputaiya</l>
<l>kāruruvaṉṟaṉ nimirtta kāl.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Going there they are the narrow lane for my heart here today,</l>
<l>in order to protect [it] from going to hot hell – the feet stretched out</l>
<l>there that day by him of cloud colour so that the form of the earth</l>
<l>and the form of the water that surrounds the earth lay covered.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
